Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:47.80,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}僅憑那種路數根本就無法追及
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:50.02,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:58.93,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以最初的一步選擇未知的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.85,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就以屬於自己的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:09.10,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以最後的一步決定世界的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:13.08,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯一的贏家非我莫屬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.61,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經親眼見證了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:22.70,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰都無從預知的最佳答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:27.62,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是在棋盤上操縱一切的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:30.24,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}掀起思考的鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:32.78,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連錯誤也是偽裝的假象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:35.28,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直至將死之前都在精心布局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.66,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是爭搶王位的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.25,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遵從想法與欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:42.76,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一次機會 在劫難逃的壞棋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:45.81,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後機會 勢必要擊潰勁敵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.80,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:50.74,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}僅憑那種路數根本就無法追及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.88,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:58.28,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}將完全勝利緊握在手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:06.10,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有人都已望塵莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.79,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:47.80,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}そんな手じゃもう追いつけない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:50.02,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:58.93,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最初の一手で選ぶ 未知なるfuture
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.85,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その有り様 this way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:09.10,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後の一手で決める 世界のanswer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:13.08,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一人のwinner it's me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.61,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}この目は見据えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:22.70,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰も未だ見通せぬ最適解を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:27.62,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全ては盤上支配するgame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:30.24,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}思考の闘争
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:32.78,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Mistakeさえも偽装して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:35.28,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Checkmateまで布石として
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.66,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Kingを奪い合うgame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.25,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}思想と欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:42.76,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}One chance 見逃さぬ悪手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:45.81,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Last chance 必ず仕留める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.80,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:50.74,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}そんな手じゃもう追いつけない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.88,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:58.28,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全勝利はこの手の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:06.10,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰にももう追いつけない
